$$\boxed{H(t_{1},t_{2},s)=\begin{cases}
f\!\left(2 t_{1},\ \dfrac{t_{2}-s/2}{1-s/2}\right)   \text{若 } 0\le t_{1}\le \dfrac{1}{2},\ \dfrac{s}{2}\le t_{2}\le 1,\\[6pt]
g\!\left(2 t_{1}-1,\ \dfrac{t_{2}}{1-s/2}\right)   \text{若 } \dfrac{1}{2}\le t_{1}\le 1,\ 0\le t_{2}\le 1-\dfrac{s}{2},\\[6pt]
x_{0}   \text{其他情况。}
\end{cases}}$$
